        Constructs a new TreeNode object.
        Parameters:
        parent - the parent of this node.
        currentState - the List of GamePlayer objects representing the current state of the game.
        currentPlayer - the current player in the game.
        round - the current round of the game.
        move - the Move used to get to this node in the game tree.
        gameTree - the GameTree that this node is a part of.
